Package org.adoxx.dobot_magician.service.response

Class DobotCoordinates

java.lang.Object
org.adoxx.dobot_magician.service.response.DobotCoordinates
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class DobotCoordinates
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Serializable indicates that the class can be converted to a bite stream and vice versa. This is quite useful for saving data or sending it between different interfaces. The roboter arm need coordinates which are based on the xyz coordinate system. X-values: the arm moves forward or backwards Y-values: the arm moves right or left Z-values: the arm moves up or down
